  "abstract": "Pigeonpea, also known as 'red gram'. is one of the major grain legume crops of the semi-Arid Tropics\r\nIt is widely grown by small farmers as a subsistence crop which helps to ensure a stable income,and which can be used In rainy and diverse ways In India, where a high percentage of the population feeds on vegetarian food, pigeonpea is an Important source of protern in human nutrition...",
